+++++++++++++++++
Log to Postgresql
+++++++++++++++++

Create the test user and database::

    $ sudo -u postgres createuser --pwprompt logtopg
    $ sudo -u postgres createdb --owner logtopg logtopg
    $ sudo -u postgres psql -c "create extension ltree";

Add to your dictConfig::

    'handlers': {
        'pg': {
            'class': 'logtopostgresql.PGHandler',
            'level': 'DEBUG',
            'logtablename': 'test_4_logs',

            'params': {
                'database': "logtopg",
                'host': "localhost",
                'user': "logtopg",
                'password': "l0gt0pg"}
        }},



